metadata.name: Pixelio #1
metadata.description: In the neon-lit realm of Binary City, a notorious figure emerged from the pixelated shadows, known as Pixelio, the 7-Bit Pixel Gangster. Pixelio was not an ordinary gangster but a master of digital manipulation, harnessing the powers of a long-lost 7-bit code that granted him unrivaled control over the digital landscape.
